@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<style>
    /* ================= ABOUT SECTION ================= */
    .about-card {
        position: relative;
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 3px solid #926950;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #2b2b2b;
    }

    .about-badge {
        position: absolute;
        top: -16px;
        left: 30px;
        background: #926950;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 6px 18px;
        border-radius: 30px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .about-card p {
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .accent {
        color: #926950;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* ================= IMAGE COLUMN ================= */
    .image-column {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;       /* SIDE BY SIDE */
        gap: 1.5rem;               /* space between images */
        justify-content: center;   /* center in column */
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-wrap: wrap;           /* wrap on small screens */
    }

    .image-column img {
        width: calc(50% - 0.75rem); /* two images side by side with gap */
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    /* ================= RESPONSIVE ================= */
    @@media (max-width: 991px) {
        .image-column {
            width: 100%;
            flex-direction: row;      /* still side by side if possible */
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .image-column img {
            width: 48%;               /* adjust to fit smaller screens */
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 576px) {
        .image-column {
            flex-direction: column;   /* stack vertically on tiny screens */
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .image-column img {
            width: 100%;
        }
    }
</style>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row align-items-start g-5">

        <!-- LEFT: ABOUT CONTENT -->
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
            <div class="about-card">
                <div class="about-badge">About Me</div>

                <p>
                    My name is <span class="accent">Daphlie Hawkins</span>, and my journey began in Haiti, where I grew up facing malnutrition—not by choice, but by circumstance. At 14, I was adopted and brought to America, a blessing I give all glory to God for, as He reminds us that His plans are to give us hope and a future.
                </p>

                <p>
                    In my first years here, I struggled with binge eating and weight gain, but my turning point came when I stepped into the gym with my church youth leader. What started as a simple act of moving my body quickly became a lifestyle that transformed me—physically, mentally, and spiritually.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Through fitness, I’ve learned that <span class="accent">consistency, motivation, and faith</span> are key to real growth. That’s why I created <span class="accent">Parfait</span>—more than a clothing brand, it’s a reminder that our bodies are God’s temple, created in His image, and already perfect.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-0">
                    My mission is to inspire women to honor their health, embrace their strength, and walk confidently in the truth that they are <span class="accent">Parfait</span> at every stage of their journey.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT: TWO IMAGES SIDE BY SIDE -->
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="~/images/company-icons/daph-one.png" alt="Parfait Image 1" />
                <img src="~/images/company-icons/daph-two.png" alt="Parfait Image 2" />
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
